snippet.textDisplay:
Standing now
calling all the people out there to stay at home 
Calling all the people out there to let us show 
that we stick together showing something beautiful

We believe 
it won't take us somewhere we're not supposed to be
It can't steal the things that God has given me 
So let's hold together and work together patiently 

It can't take us down
It can't break us down
It can't take us down

Stay at home 
We will keep on fighting here so stay at home 
we will win the fight for you so let us know 
we can stick together showing something beautiful
